y 20, 2001</td>\n<td>January 31, 2005</td>\n<td rowspan="2"><a href="/wiki/George_W._Bush" title="George W. Bush">George W. Bush</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Samuel_W._Bodman" class="mw-redirect" title="Samuel W. Bodman">Samuel W. Bodman</a></td>\n<td>February 1, 2005</td>\n<td>January 20, 2009</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12</td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Steven_Chu" title="Steven Chu">Steven Chu</a></td>\n<td>January 21, 2009</td>\n<td>April 22, 2013</td>\n<td rowspan="2"><a href="/wiki/Barack_Obama" title="Barack Obama">Barack Obama</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13</td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Ernest_Moniz" title="Ernest Moniz">Ernest Moniz</a></td>\n<td>May 16, 2013</td>\n<td>January 20, 2017</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14</td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Rick_Perry" title="Rick Perry">Rick Perry</a></td>\n<td>March 2, 2017</td>\n<td><i>Incumbent</i></td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Donald_Trump" title="Donald Trump">Donald Trump</a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="See_also">See also</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=United_States_Department_of_Energy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: See also">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role="navigation" aria-label="Portals" class="noprint portal plainlist tright" style="margin:0.5em 0 0.5em 1em;border:solid #aaa 1px">\n<ul style="display:table;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0.1em;max-width:175px;background:#f9f9f9;font-size:85%;line-height:110%;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold">\n<li style="display:table-row"><span style="display:table-cell;padding:0.2em;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5c/Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_%28obverse%29.svg/28px-Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_%28obverse%29.svg.png" width="28" height="28" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5c/Great_Seal_